rComments: Chan is an excellent professor.  Cares about students' learning!  Is very exciting about teaching and it shows.  I learned so much from her.  Excellent!
Goes above and beyond to help you "get it." Made herself very available to answer questions, make suggestions and offer encouragement. Fabulous teacher!

She understands the importance of connecting previous knowledge to new. She made the dense and challenging readings clear with her well prepared weekly lectures. She gave enormous space for professionals to incorporate the activity of the class with their professional challenges in the real world. Overall, she was one of the best instructors ever!

Chan is an excellent Professor.  She always had a helpful suggestion and challenged Instructors to consider new ways of teaching and why we use the methods we do.  Plus, it is hard to "teach" teachers.  BRAVO!
